Mark Sheptoff Financial Planning LLC Increases Stake in Colgate-Palmolive Company (CL)
Paterniano Del Favero
Luglio 22, 2017



Condividere













During the same quarter previous year, the firm posted $0.70 earnings per share. S&P Research maintained Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) on Monday, November 2 with "Hold" rating. Gould Asset Mgmt Ca reported 5,016 shares. Verduin Patricia also sold $282,070 worth of Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) on Wednesday, March 15. It has underperformed by 10.47% the S&P500.The move comes after 8 months positive chart setup for the $64.52B company. We have $77.86 PT which if reached, will make NYSE:CL worth $3.87B more.Since February 2, 2017, it had 0 insider buys, and 20 selling transactions for $17.03 million activity. Another trade for 14,000 shares valued at $932,999 was made by HUSTON JOHN J on Friday, February 10. KOGAN RICHARD J sold 8,000 shares worth $575,350.Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) shares saw a recent bid of $72.09 and 3.61M shares have exchanged hands in the recent trading session, yielding a -0.19% decline over the past week.CL price decreased -0.55% or $0.4 versus $72.49 at the end of the prior session. Zacks Investment Research upgraded Colgate-Palmolive from a "hold" rating to a "buy" rating and set a $83.00 target price on the stock in a research report on Tuesday, July 4th. SADOVE STEPHEN I sold $527,971 worth of stock. The business had revenue of $3.83 billion during the quarter, compared to analyst estimates of $3.89 billion. Colgate-Palmolive has $88 highest and $65 lowest target. The stock's 50 day moving average price is $74.80 and its 200-day moving average price is $72.20. Colgate-Palmolive had 41 analyst reports since July 21, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel.Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) posted its quarterly earnings results on Friday. Jefferies maintained it with "Hold" rating and $7700 target in Thursday, July 6 report. The firm has "Neutral" rating given on Friday, July 29 by UBS. Zacks Investment Research upgraded Colgate-Palmolive from a "sell" rating to a "hold" rating in a research note on Friday, March 24th. They set a "hold" rating and a $78.00 price target on the stock. Wells Fargo reinitiated the stock with "Market Perform" rating in Tuesday, November 15 report. The rating was downgraded by Citigroup to "Neutral" on Monday, January 30. Stifel Nicolaus maintained the shares of CL in report on Monday, January 30 with "Hold" rating.Investors sentiment decreased to 0.86 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.05, from 0.96 in 2016Q3. Rathbone Brothers Plc acquired 33,018 shares as Colgate (CL)'s stock rose 3.95%. State Board Of Administration Of Florida Retirement System reported 1.28 million shares stake. Valley Natl Advisers holds 0.02% or 670 shares. Nbt Bancorp N A Ny accumulated 0.85% or 75,528 shares. Orrstown Financial Services owns 2,725 shares or 0.18% of their USA portfolio. Allianz Asset Mngmt Ag stated it has 1.10 million shares or 0.06% of all its holdings. First Hawaiian Comml Bank reported 12,984 shares stake. It also upped Synopsys Inc (NASDAQ:SNPS) stake by 84,106 shares and now owns 932,772 shares. About shares traded. Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) has risen 6.23% since July 21, 2016 and is uptrending. 1,797 were accumulated by Blue Chip Prtnrs.Shares of Colgate-Palmolive Company (CL) traded up 1.64% during trading on Friday, hitting $73.27. St Germain D J owns 3,425 shares or 0.03% of their U.S. portfolio. Soros Fund Limited Liability Corp holds 0.94% of its portfolio in Facebook Inc (NASDAQ:FB) for 353,686 shares. Finemark Commercial Bank & Tru reported 29,631 shares or 0.16% of all its holdings. Brown Brothers Harriman And reported 91,605 shares. Colgate Palmolive Co now has $62.82 billion valuation. The Company, through its Hill's Pet Nutrition segment, manufactures pet nutrition products for dogs and cats with products marketed in over 80 countries across the world.Oral, personal and home care revenue slipped to $3.25bn, from $3.27 billion, missing consensus of $3.32 billion. It has a 28.8 P/E ratio. The Oral, Personal and Home Care product segment is operated through five geographic segments, which include North America, Latin America, Europe, Asia Pacific and Africa/Eurasia. State Street Corp is the second biggest holder with 61 million shares now valued at 4.43 B million whilst Fidelity Management and Research Company has 33 million shares valued at 2.40 B million.Several other hedge funds also recently added to or reduced their stakes in CL. Advantage Investment Management LLC bought a new position in Colgate-Palmolive during the fourth quarter worth $104,000. Pfizer Inc (NYSE:PFE) was reduced too. One research analyst has rated the stock with a sell rating, thirteen have assigned a hold rating and three have given a buy rating to the stock. Therefore 60% are positive. Facebook had 136 analyst reports since July 21, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The rating was upgraded by Craig Hallum on Thursday, December 8 to "Buy". The firm earned "Neutral" rating on Monday, May 2 by Goldman Sachs. As per Friday, June 9, the company rating was maintained by Jefferies.Receive News & Ratings Via Email - Enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts' ratings with our FREE daily email newsletter.

 




